data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home. Situated in a tranquil neighborhood, this home boasts a meticulously updated interior with a focus on both style and functionality. This property includes many recent updates including a brand new roof, all new flooring, new smart appliances, new quartz counter tops and so much more! Step into the heart of the home, where an open floor plan creates a sense of spaciousness and connectivity. The fully updated kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring brand new quartz countertops and all new smart appliances. The waterproof laminate flooring, adorned with a lifetime warranty, not only adds a touch of elegance but also ensures durability that stands the test of time. The spacious primary bedroom is a true retreat, offering a generous space to unwind and relax. Revel in the convenience of a walk-in closet that caters to your storage needs. The ensuite master bathroom includes a large soaking tub, shower and toilet room. Entertain and enjoy the outdoors on the large back deck, a perfect venue for gatherings with family and friends. Immerse yourself in the soothing waters of the hot tub, creating a serene atmosphere for relaxation under the open sky. Conveniently located just 6 minutes away from the shores of Lake Erie, this residence offers a perfect blend of suburban tranquility and proximity to nature. Whether you're seeking a weekend retreat or a permanent residence, this home is designed to elevate your living experience.
